            (gen_random_uuid(), 'Restore Old Photo', 'generate-media/mini-tools/restore-old-photo.png', 'image-mini-tools', 'Restore this old damaged photograph with maximum realism. Repair scratches, cracks, stains, fading, and missing areas while preserving the subject''s exact identity, facial structure, age, expression, pose, clothing, and background. Maintain original lighting, era-accurate texture, natural skin detail, and authentic film grain. No modernization. Archival-quality photo restoration. Negative Prompt: Blurry, low-resolution, AI look, beautification, smooth plastic skin, identity change, altered face, cartoon, CGI, HDR, over-saturated colors, over-sharpened, modern styling, makeup, extra limbs, deformed anatomy, text artifacts, watermarks', '2025-12-18 08:23:02.287083 +00:00', '2025-12-18 08:23:02.287083 +00:00'),
            (gen_random_uuid(), 'Replace Object', 'generate-media/mini-tools/replace-object.png', 'image-mini-tools', 'Replace the object in the original photo with the uploaded reference object. Preserve the original scene, subject identity, camera angle, perspective, scale, depth, lighting direction, shadows, reflections, and color balance. Match the replacement object''s shape, material, texture, color, proportions, and surface details exactly to the reference. Ensure natural integration: correct contact shadows, realistic occlusion, accurate edge blending, and consistent light temperature. Maintain full photorealism, sharp focus, natural textures, and true-to-life proportions. Professional, seamless object replacement with no visible edit traces. NEGATIVE PROMPT (MANDATORY): Blurry, low-resolution, soft focus, identity change, altered subject, incorrect scale, wrong perspective, mismatched lighting, inconsistent shadows, floating object, poor edge blending, halos, artifacts, noise, over-sharpened, plastic texture, cartoon, CGI, illustration, HDR, distorted geometry, extra objects, missing parts, color bleeding, text, watermark, logo.', now(), null),
