            (gen_random_uuid(), 'Pixel', 'generate-media/image/pixel.png', 'image', 'Pixel art full-body character of [subject], front-facing idle pose, chibi proportions, large expressive eyes, simplified facial features, clean 16-bit RPG sprite style, soft pixel shading, limited color palette, crisp pixel edges, subtle highlight and shadow, centered on plain neutral background, nostalgic game character aesthetic. Negative Prompt: blurry, low-resolution, smooth gradients, anti-aliasing, photorealistic, 3D render, anime illustration, vector art, over-detailed textures, extra limbs, deformed anatomy, text artifacts.', now(), null),
            (gen_random_uuid(), 'Group Photo', 'generate-media/mini-tools/group-photo.png', 'image-mini-tools', 'Merge all subjects from the uploaded photos into a single, cohesive group photo. Preserve each person''s exact identity, including face structure, skin tone, age, hairstyle, body shape, proportions, and facial features. Maintain realistic scale between subjects. Place all subjects naturally together in one shared scene with consistent lighting, color balance, sharp focus, and perspective. Ensure clean edges around hair, hands, and clothing. Photorealistic result only. High clarity, natural textures, true-to-life details. Professional group portrait quality. Negative Prompt (Mandatory): Blurry, low-resolution, soft focus, identity change, face alteration, mixed facial features, incorrect proportions, size mismatch, distorted anatomy, extra limbs, missing fingers, deformed faces, plastic skin, beauty retouching, cartoon, CGI, HDR, over-sharpened, noise, artifacts, mismatched lighting, color inconsistency, halos, rough edges, background artifacts, text, watermark, logo.', now(), null),
