            (gen_random_uuid(), 'Miniature', 'generate-media/image/miniature.png', 'image', 'Hyper-realistic miniature diorama of [subject], portrayed as a small-scale world with tiny human figurines actively interacting with it (building, repairing, exploring). Macro photography look, shallow depth of field, realistic scale contrast, detailed textures, soft natural light, cinematic realism, playful yet believable, premium handcrafted miniature style. Negative Prompt: blurry, low-resolution, distorted scale, extra limbs, deformed figures, unrealistic textures, cartoonish, anime, CGI plastic look, over-sharpened, noise, text artifacts.', now(), null),
            (gen_random_uuid(), 'Clay', 'generate-media/image/clay.png', 'image', 'Handcrafted claymation / stop-motion style version of attached [subject], clearly a clay puppet with a slightly oversized head, big expressive eyes, simplified facial features, visible clay texture and subtle fingerprints, matte painted surface, sculpted clay hair, soft fabric-like clay clothing, whimsical emotional look, shallow depth of field, soft cinematic studio lighting, eye-level shot, premium stop-motion film quality. Negative Prompt: blurry, low-res, photorealistic skin, pores, hyper realism, CGI render, glossy plastic, anime, flat cartoon, extra limbs, deformed face, harsh lighting, noise, text artifacts.', now(), null),
            (gen_random_uuid(), 'AI Extended Image', 'generate-media/mini-tools/ai-extended-image.png', 'image-mini-tools', 'Extend the uploaded image naturally. Preserve exact subject identity, face, body proportions, pose, camera angle, perspective, and lighting. Seamless background expansion with matching depth, textures, colors, and shadows. Photorealistic only. Negative Prompt: Blurry, low-resolution, identity change, face alteration, body reshaping, pose change, lighting mismatch, perspective distortion, AI artifacts, unrealistic textures, plastic skin, CGI, cartoon, HDR, over-sharpened, extra limbs, deformed anatomy, text, logos, watermarks.', now(), null),
            (gen_random_uuid(), 'Enhance Image', 'generate-media/mini-tools/enhance-image.png', 'image-mini-tools', 'Enhance the provided photograph with maximum realism and fidelity. Improve overall sharpness, clarity, and detail while strictly preserving the subject''s original identity, facial structure, age, expression, pose, clothing, and environment. Correct lighting balance, contrast, and color accuracy without altering the original mood or era. Refine skin texture naturally, maintain authentic textures and materials, and retain realistic depth and perspective. Output should look like a professionally enhanced original photo, not AI-generated. Negative Prompt: Blurry, low-resolution, AI look, identity change, altered face, beautification, smooth plastic skin, over-sharpened, HDR, over-saturated colors, cartoon, CGI, artifacts, halos, noise, banding, extra limbs, deformed anatomy, text artifacts, watermarks.', now(), null),
