            (gen_random_uuid(), 'Clothing Change', 'generate-media/mini-tools/clothing-change.png', 'image-mini-tools', 'Change the subject''s clothing to exactly match the uploaded clothing reference (or described outfit). Preserve the person''s exact identity, face, body shape, age, skin tone, hairstyle, expression, pose, camera angle, framing, background, and lighting. Apply realistic fabric texture, natural folds, correct garment fit and scale, seamless integration. Photorealistic result only. Negative Prompt: Identity change, face alteration, body reshaping, pose change, background change, lighting change, blurry, low-resolution, AI artifacts, unrealistic fabric, plastic skin, cartoon, CGI, HDR, over-sharpened, extra limbs, deformed anatomy, text, logos, watermarks.', now(), null),
            (gen_random_uuid(), 'Photo Style Change', 'generate-media/mini-tools/photo-style-change.png', 'image-mini-tools', 'Change the photo style to a different artistic or photographic style while keeping the subject consistent.', now(), null),
            (gen_random_uuid(), 'Professional ID Photo', 'generate-media/mini-tools/professional-id-photo.png', 'image-mini-tools', 'A professional biometric passport/ID photo of the same person from the uploaded original. Subject facing directly forward, neutral expression, eyes open and clearly visible, mouth closed. Head centered and upright, shoulders squared, straight posture. Plain solid white or light gray background, evenly lit. Natural skin tone, realistic facial texture, no beauty retouching. Soft, diffused studio lighting from the front, minimal shadows. Sharp focus, high clarity, true-to-life proportions. Photorealistic, government-compliant ID photo style. Negative Prompt: Blur, low resolution, noise, harsh shadows, uneven lighting, background texture, gradients, patterns, props, accessories, hats, sunglasses, smile, exaggerated expression, beauty retouching, smooth plastic skin, face reshaping, identity change, age change, pose change, head tilt, camera angle change, distortion, cartoon, CGI, HDR, over-sharpening, color cast, text, watermark, logo.', now(), null),
            (gen_random_uuid(), 'AI Filters & Edit', 'generate-media/mini-tools/ai-filters-edit.png', 'image-mini-tools', 'Apply the exact visual style from the uploaded reference photo(s) onto the original photo. Preserve the original subject''s full identity: face structure, age, skin tone, body shape, hairstyle, expression, pose, and proportions must remain unchanged. Transfer only: Color grading | Lighting direction & contrast | Exposure & tonal balance | Mood & atmosphere | Texture finish (film, matte, clean, cinematic, etc.). Match: Light temperature & intensity | Shadow softness & highlight roll-off | Color palette & saturation level | Overall visual mood. Maintain photorealism, natural skin texture, sharp focus, realistic depth, and consistent perspective. No stylization beyond what exists in the reference. Professional, high-quality photo result. NEGATIVE PROMPT (MANDATORY): Identity change, face alteration, age change, skin smoothing, beauty retouching, plastic skin, CGI, cartoon, illustration, painterly effect, HDR, over-stylized look, exaggerated colors, incorrect lighting direction, mismatched shadows, blur, low resolution, noise, artifacts, halos, distorted anatomy, extra limbs, missing fingers, warped proportions, text, watermark, logo.', now(), null),
            (gen_random_uuid(), '3D Figure', 'generate-media/image/3d-figure.png', 'image', 'A high-quality collectible figurine display scene of [subject], clearly presented as a manufactured premium figure, standing on a clear acrylic display base. The figure has smooth matte painted vinyl skin, simplified facial features, and fully sculpted hair and clothing with clean molded details. Placed on a modern work desk in a creative studio environment, with a computer monitor in the background showing 3D modeling software or a wireframe character, reinforcing the toy-design process. A retail-style product box featuring the same character stands nearby. Photorealistic product photography, eye-level shot, 50mm lens, soft natural indoor lighting, shallow depth of field, sharp focus on the figure, premium commercial quality. Negative Prompt: blurry, low-res, deformed face, extra limbs, unrealistic skin, pores, human realism, cartoonish, anime, over-sharpened, noise, text artifacts', now(), null),
            (gen_random_uuid(), 'Blueprint', 'generate-media/image/blueprint.png', 'image', 'A highly detailed technical blueprint illustration of [subject], front-facing and perfectly centered, rendered as a precision-engineered design study. The subject is drawn with clean graphite-style linework and subtle cross-hatching, overlaid with red technical annotations, measurement lines, and schematic callouts. Neutral warm parchment background filled with architectural sketches, exploded diagrams, and handwritten engineering notes. Symmetrical composition, calm and analytical mood, premium concept-art quality, ultra-sharp detail, realistic proportions, no abstraction. NEGATIVE PROMPT: blurry, low-resolution, distorted proportions, extra limbs, deformed anatomy, cartoonish, anime, painterly brushstrokes, photorealistic skin, CGI render, noisy background, messy lines, over-stylized colors, text artifacts.', now(), null),
            (gen_random_uuid(), 'Fish eyes', 'generate-media/image/fish-eyes.png', 'image', 'A high-contrast, bright futuristic portrait photographed of [subject] with a Hasselblad medium-format film camera using an extreme fisheye wide-angle lens and harsh on-camera flash. The space is constructed from glossy white floor panels that reflect light, and a gridded white ceiling emitting uniform illumination. The scene feels clinical, sci-fi, and minimalistic.', now(), null);
